            <title>[SHIRO-177] Wron SimpleCookie expires locale</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHIRO-177</link>
                <project id="12310950" key="SHIRO">Shiro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SimpleCookie.toCookieDate method to format cookie uses default locale. My default locale ru_RU. When browser receive cookie with expires formatted in non en_US locale, browser set cookie expires=session.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Resolutiojon of this trouble is: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    private static String toCookieDate(Date date) &lt;/p&gt;
{
        TimeZone tz = TimeZone.getTimeZone(GMT_TIME_ZONE_ID);
        DateFormat fmt = new SimpleDateFormat(COOKIE_DATE_FORMAT_STRING, Locale.US);
        fmt.setTimeZone(tz);
        return fmt.format(date);
    }</description>
